data.description: This beautiful brick ranch home sits in a quiet subdivision in Laurel County, but within minutes of all the conveniences of the city. Some of the home attributes include a spacious eat in kitchen equipped with a refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher, and a brand new range. The sliding barn door separates the kitchen from the utility room and a full bathroom. The living room is spacious and boasts a beautiful built in electric fireplace. This home has 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms! This property is very convenient to town, 1.2 miles to London Country Club, 2.5 miles (5 minutes) to the hospital, 1.9 miles (4 minutes) to the interstate, shopping, and restaurants. As a bonus, the home comes with a nice sized storage shed. This property is within the South Laurel School District. This home is perfect for anyone wanting to be close to town, but away from it all.
